fields.description: Indicates that the region is restricted for Cloud PC CPU provisioning. True indicates that Cloud PC provisioning with CPU isn't available in this region. false indicates that it's available. The default value is false. Read-only.
fields.name: CPURestricted

fields.description: Indicates that the region is restricted for Cloud PC GPU provisioning. True indicates that Cloud PC provisioning with GPU isn't available in this region. false indicates that it's available. The default value is false. Read-only.

fields.description: Indicates that the region is restricted for Cloud PC nested virtualization provisioning. True indicates that Cloud PC provisioning with nested virtualization isn't available in this region; false indicates that it's available. The default value is false. Read-only.
fields.name: NestedVirtualizationRestricted
